OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FA teenage girl has been sentenced for
OL,7,Fattempted murder after she lured a 15-
OL,8,Fyear-old boy to a park before he was
OL,9,Fstabbed.
OL,11,FTwo teenage boys were also sentenced
OL,12,Ffor causing grievous bodily harm with
OL,13,Fintent.
OL,15,FThe victim was stabbed during the
OL,16,Fattack at Herrington County Park, in
OL,17,FSunderland on 6 June, 2025.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
