OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FAn investigation by Northumbria Police
OL,7,Ffound the girl, now aged 16, had lured
OL,8,Fthe victim to the park before one of
OL,9,Fthe boys stabbed him.
OL,11,FAll three suspects were subsequently
OL,12,Fcharged with attempted murder, with
OL,13,Fthe girl then admitting the offence in
OL,14,Fa hearing at Newcastle Crown Court.
OL,16,FBoth boys admitted grievous bodily
OL,17,Fharm with intent but denied attempted
OL,18,Fmurder.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FThey stood trial over the attempted
OL,7,Fmurder charge against them in November
OL,8,F2025 and were both found not guilty
OL,9,Ffollowing a trial, also held at
OL,10,FNewcastle Crown Court.
OL,12,FOn Friday (17 April), all three
OL,13,Fdefendants ` who cannot be named for
OL,14,Flegal reasons ` were sentenced.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FThe teenage girl was sentenced to
OL,7,Fseven years and four months in youth
OL,8,Fdetention. One of the boys who
OL,9,Fadmitted grievous bodily harm was
OL,10,Fsentenced to two years and 10 months
OL,11,Fin youth detention, while the other
OL,12,Fwas sentenced to a 24-month detention
OL,13,Fand training order.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
