OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FFollowing the teenagers' sentencing,
OL,7,Fthe officer in charge of the
OL,8,Finvestigation, Detective Inspector
OL,9,FJohn Hopkins, of Northumbria Police's
OL,10,FSunderland Criminal Investigation
OL,11,FDepartment, said: "The victim in this
OL,12,Fincident has been through a truly
OL,13,Fhorrendous ordeal.
OL,15,F"We hope now the case has concluded
OL,16,Fand those responsible have been
OL,17,Fsentenced that he and his family are
OL,18,Fable to take some closure from the
OL,19,Fevents of the past 10 months."
OL,26,@sD@SOUwD@AOU{D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/8
