OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,FDet Insp Hopkins added: "The actions
OL,7,Fof the three offenders involved in
OL,8,Fthis case were abhorrent and the
OL,9,Fvictim is extremely fortunate not to
OL,10,Fhave died.
OL,12,F"Thanks to the hard work and
OL,13,Fdedication of our officers who carried
OL,14,Fout such a thorough investigation, we
OL,15,Fhave now been able to secure
OL,16,Fconvictions against those responsible.
OL,18,F"I sincerely hope that this case
OL,19,Fserves as a reminder of the serious
OL,20,Fharm that carrying knives can do.
OL,26,@nD@YOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,422,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F421A1776456351
OL,3,CGirl, 16, lured boy to park before he
OL,4,Cwas stabbed
OL,6,F"We would ask that parents in our
OL,7,Fregion who have concerns that the
OL,8,Fyoung people they care for may be
OL,9,Fgetting involved in knife crime to
OL,10,Fhave those difficult conversations
OL,11,Fabout the extreme dangers that come
OL,12,Fwith deciding to arm yourself with a
OL,13,Fweapon.
OL,15,F"In no way does carrying a knife
OL,16,Fprotect you, in fact it puts you and
OL,17,Fothers around you potentially in
OL,18,Fharm's way and can have a devastating
OL,19,Fimpact on your life and the lives of
OL,20,Fmany others in the process."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU|D@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/8
